ion (leftward or backward)','A calculation error','C',5,0,0,5),(1260,'Kerala',9,'English','Maths','MCQ',1,'7','Negative Numbers',17,'Displacement','Using the rules x + (-y) = x - y and x - (-y) = x + y, simplify: a - (-b) - (-c) - d:','a - b - c - d','a + b + c - d','a - b + c - d','a + b - c - d','B',5,0,0,5),(1261,'Kerala',9,'English','Maths','MCQ',1,'7','Negative Numbers',17,'Time and Speed','In the context of speed and direction, a negative speed means:','The object is stationary','The object is moving in the opposite direction','The object has slowed down','Speed cannot be negative','B',1,0,0,1),(1262,'Kerala',9,'English','Maths','MCQ',1,'7','Negative Numbers',17,'Time and Speed','(-x) × (-y) equals:','#NAME?','xy','#NAME?','x/y','B',1,0,0,1),(1263,'Kerala',9,'English','Maths','MCQ',1,'7','Negative Numbers',17,'Time and Speed','(-3) × (-4) =','-12','12','7','-7','B',1,0,0,1),(1264,'Kerala',9,'English','Maths','MCQ',1,'7','Negative Numbers',17,'Time and Speed','(-5) × 6 =','30','-1','-30','1','C',1,0,0,1),(1265,'Kerala',9,'English','Maths','MCQ',1,'7','Negative Numbers',17,'Time and Speed','An object moves at speed -4 m/s (leftward) for 3 seconds. Its displacement is:','12 m to the right','-12 m (12 m to the left)','-4/3 m','7 m','B',2,0,0,2),(1266,'Kerala',9,'English','Maths','MCQ',1,'7','Negative Numbers',17,'Time and Speed','An object with speed -3 m/s moves for -5 seconds (back in time). Its displacement = s×t = (-3)×(-5) =','-15 m','15 m','8 m','-8 m','B',2,0,0,2),(1267,'Kerala',9,'English','Maths','MCQ',1,'7','Negative Numbers',17,'Time and Speed','Compute (-2) × 7 × (-3):','-42','42','-12','12','B',2,0,0,2),(1268,'Kerala',9,'English','Maths','MCQ',1,'7','Negative Numbers',17,'Time and Speed','The product of an even number of negative factors is:','Negative','Positive','Zero','Undefined','B',2,0,0,2),(1269,'Kerala',9,'English','Maths','MCQ',1,'7','Negative Numbers',17,'Time and Speed','A car moves at -60 km/h (west). In 2.5 hours, its displacement is:','15