io of their bases?','1:04','4:05','1:05','4:01','C',2,0,0,2),(1546,'Kerala',9,'English','Maths','MCQ',1,'3','Parallel Lines',13,'Triangle Division','In triangle ABC, DE || BC. AD = 6, AB = 10. Find DE if BC = 15:','6','9','10','12','B',3,0,0,3),(1547,'Kerala',9,'English','Maths','MCQ',1,'3','Parallel Lines',13,'Triangle Division','In triangle ABC, a line parallel to BC meets AB at D with AD:DB = 2:3. If AE = 8 cm on AC, find EC:','8 cm','12 cm','16 cm','6 cm','B',3,0,0,3),(1548,'Kerala',9,'English','Maths','MCQ',1,'3','Parallel Lines',13,'Triangle Division','A line cuts two sides of triangle PQR parallel to QR. PX = 4, PY = 5. If PQ = 12, find PR:','10','12','15','20','C',3,0,0,3),(1549,'Kerala',9,'English','Maths','MCQ',1,'3','Parallel Lines',13,'Triangle Division','In triangle ABC, DE || BC. The perimeter of triangle ADE is 18 cm and the ratio AD:AB = 1:3. What is the perimeter of triangle ABC?','36 cm','54 cm','27 cm','45 cm','B',3,0,0,3),(1550,'Kerala',9,'English','Maths','MCQ',1,'3','Parallel Lines',13,'Triangle Division','In triangle ABC, DE || BC where D is on AB, E is on AC. If AD/AB = 2/5, what fraction of the triangle''s area does triangle ADE have compared to ABC?','5-Feb','25-Apr','5-Apr','25-Feb','B',3,0,0,3),(1551,'Kerala',9,'English','Maths','MCQ',1,'3','Parallel Lines',13,'Triangle Division','In triangle ABC, D is on AB and E is on AC such that DE || BC. BD = 6, AD = 4, AE = 5. Find CE:','6','7.5','8','10','B',4,0,0,4),(1552,'Kerala',9,'English','Maths','MCQ',1,'3','Parallel Lines',13,'Triangle Division','Two lines are drawn inside triangle ABC, both parallel to BC. They divide AB into three equal parts. What ratio do they divide AC into?','1:02:03','1:01:01','2:03:04','1:02','B',4,0,0,4),(1553,'Kerala',9,'English','Maths','MCQ',1,'3','Parallel Lines',13,'Triangle Division','In triangle ABC, DE || BC with D on AB and E on AC. AD = x, DB = 2x, AE = y. Express EC in terms of y:','y','2y','y/2','3y','B',4,0,0,4),(1554,'Kerala',9,'English','Maths','MCQ',