glish','Physics','MCQ',1,'4','Gravitation',21,'Mass and Weight','On Earth (g = 9.8 m/s²) an object weighs 196 N. The object is moved to a planet where it weighs 78.4 N. What is g on that planet?','3.92 m/s²','7.84 m/s²','39.2 m/s²','1.96 m/s²','A',5,0,0,5),(1851,'Kerala',9,'English','Physics','MCQ',1,'4','Gravitation',21,'Pressure','Pressure is defined as:','Force multiplied by area','Mass divided by volume','Force per unit area','Area divided by force','C',1,0,0,1),(1852,'Kerala',9,'English','Physics','MCQ',1,'4','Gravitation',21,'Pressure','The SI unit of pressure is:','Newton','Pascal (Pa)','kg/m³','N·m','B',1,0,0,1),(1853,'Kerala',9,'English','Physics','MCQ',1,'4','Gravitation',21,'Pressure','One Pascal equals:','1 N/m','1 N·m²','1 N/m²','1 kg/m²','C',1,0,0,1),(1854,'Kerala',9,'English','Physics','MCQ',1,'4','Gravitation',21,'Pressure','A sharp knife cuts more easily than a blunt knife because:','Sharp knife has more force','Sharp knife has less area — greater pressure for same force','Sharp knife is heavier','Blunt knife is slippery','B',1,0,0,1),(1855,'Kerala',9,'English','Physics','MCQ',1,'4','Gravitation',21,'Pressure','Pressure in a fluid acts:','Only downward','Only upward','Equally in all directions','Only horizontally','C',2,0,0,2),(1856,'Kerala',9,'English','Physics','MCQ',1,'4','Gravitation',21,'Pressure','A person stands on a floor with total weight 600 N, both feet flat (area 0.04 m²). Pressure on floor is:','15000 Pa','24 Pa','240 Pa','150 Pa','A',2,0,0,2),(1857,'Kerala',9,'English','Physics','MCQ',1,'4','Gravitation',21,'Pressure','If the same force is applied over a larger area, the pressure:','Increases','Remains the same','Decreases','Doubles','C',2,0,0,2),(1858,'Kerala',9,'English','Physics','MCQ',1,'4','Gravitation',21,'Pressure','Pressure in a liquid column of height h, density ρ, and g is given by:','P = ρ/gh','P = ρgh','P = gh/ρ','P = g/ρh','B',2,0,0,2),(1859,'Kerala',9,'English','Physics','MCQ',1,'4','Gravitation',21,'Pressure','A force of