he same direction','An equal and opposite reaction','A larger reaction','A smaller reaction in the same direction','B',1,0,0,1),(1952,'Kerala',9,'English','Physics','MCQ',1,'3','Laws of Motion',20,'Newton''s Third Law of Motion','Action and reaction forces in Newton''s Third Law act on:','The same object','Different objects','Objects moving in the same direction','Objects at rest only','B',1,0,0,1),(1953,'Kerala',9,'English','Physics','MCQ',1,'3','Laws of Motion',20,'Newton''s Third Law of Motion','When you push a wall with 10 N, the wall pushes back with:','5 N','0 N','More than 10 N','10 N in the opposite direction','D',1,0,0,1),(1954,'Kerala',9,'English','Physics','MCQ',1,'3','Laws of Motion',20,'Newton''s Third Law of Motion','A swimmer pushes backward against the water. The water pushes the swimmer:','Downward','Backward','Forward','Sideways','C',1,0,0,1),(1955,'Kerala',9,'English','Physics','MCQ',1,'3','Laws of Motion',20,'Newton''s Third Law of Motion','A gun recoils when fired because of:','Newton''s First Law','Newton''s Second Law','Newton''s Third Law — bullet is pushed forward and gun is pushed backward','Gravity','C',2,0,0,2),(1956,'Kerala',9,'English','Physics','MCQ',1,'3','Laws of Motion',20,'Newton''s Third Law of Motion','A rocket in space propels itself forward by:','Pushing against air','Pulling itself by an anchor','Expelling gases backward, which pushes the rocket forward','Using gravity from nearby objects','C',2,0,0,2),(1957,'Kerala',9,'English','Physics','MCQ',1,'3','Laws of Motion',20,'Newton''s Third Law of Motion','When a person jumps off a boat onto a dock, the boat moves:','Forward','Stationary','Backward','In the same direction as the person','C',2,0,0,2),(1958,'Kerala',9,'English','Physics','MCQ',1,'3','Laws of Motion',20,'Newton''s Third Law of Motion','Which pair are action-reaction forces when a ball falls under gravity?','Earth''s gravity on ball and friction on ball','Earth''s gravity on ball and ball''s gravity on Earth','Normal 