,'A 3 kg trolley at rest is hit by a 1 kg ball at 12 m/s. They move together. A friction force of 2 N then decelerates them. Distance they travel before stopping is:','9 m','3 m','6 m','18 m','A',5,0,0,5),(2000,'Kerala',9,'English','Physics','MCQ',1,'3','Laws of Motion',20,'Law of Conservation of Momentum','An object of mass 2 kg (velocity 3 m/s east) collides with an object of mass 1 kg (velocity 6 m/s west). After the perfectly inelastic collision, the combined object moves:','1 m/s east','0 m/s (they stop)','1 m/s west','4.5 m/s east','B',5,0,0,5);
